B-Eng. HB 4084
1 (c) Alignment with adopted local, regional or statewide economic development strategies,
2 land-use plans, infrastructure plans, workforce strategies or climate and energy transition
3 goals, where enterprise zone designation would materially advance implementation;
4 (d) Demonstrated opportunity to:
5 (A) Support emerging, traded sector or innovation-driven industries;
6 (B) Retain, reinvest in or modernize existing industries or facilities; or
