8 or workforce quality;
9 (e) Commitment by the zone sponsor to a performance-based development approach, in-
10 cluding measurable objectives related to capital investment, wages, workforce development,
11 retention or modernization outcomes, productivity improvement, redevelopment outcomes
12 or other economic performance indicators established by the Oregon Business Development
13 Department by rule; or
14 (f) Other community-defined indicators of economic need or development potential sup-
